						<p class="stext-113 cl6 p-b-26">
                            Once upon a time, in a world where fashion trends were dictated by a select few, there was a little company called Trendly. Trendly was started by a group of passionate fashion enthusiasts who believed that everyone had the right to express themselves through their clothing and accessories. They wanted to challenge the status quo and create a space where people could explore their personal style without judgment.
                            With their motto, "time to change," the Trendly team set out to revolutionize the fashion industry. They traveled the world, sourcing unique pieces from up-and-coming designers and established fashion houses alike. They handpicked items that were not only stylish but also sustainable, ensuring that they were doing their part for the planet.
						</p>

						<p class="stext-113 cl6 p-b-26">
